cs.LG, cs.NA, cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.CV 

The paper focuses on improving the training of deep neural networks, which is a core topic in machine learning and falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the use of neural networks for solving partial differential equations, which is a common application in the field of numerical analysis (cs.NA). Additionally, the paper proposes novel initialization techniques and optimization algorithms, which are relevant to the fields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computational intelligence (cs.SI). Finally, the paper provides numerical examples of improved accuracy in image classification, which is a common application of deep learning in computer vision (cs.CV).
